We discuss the success of ROC clinching the women’s team gold medal in #artisticgymnastics with Olympic champions @lauriehernandez @shannonmiller96 , Olympics gymnastics producer @sbregman87 and host @ash_tulloch.

Find out their thoughts on how USA won silver behind ROC, with Team GB taking bronze. We also look ahead to the women’s all around coming up later this week. 

#strongertogether @figymnastics

node.text:
We speak with @angeliquekidjo about performing a rendition of the iconic anthem - Imagine, for the #tokyo2020 Opening Ceremony.

She shares her joy in seeing @naomiosaka lighting the Olympic flame and looks forward to world uniting through peace in sport for the next 16 days of Olympic competition.

#strongertogether
